---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Fast Web Guru"
  description="How Fast Web Guru collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information, in line with the Australian Privacy Principles."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-dark py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-white mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl leading-relaxed">We collect only what we need to deliver and support your website — and we never sell your data. Here's exactly how we handle your information.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy content -->
  <section class="section-light section-pad">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Fast Web Guru is an Australian-owned website hosting and support service. This policy explains how we handle personal information in accordance with the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth) and the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs). "We", "us", and "our" refer to Fast Web Guru.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">We collect information you provide directly — your name, email address, phone number, business name, and website URL — when you request an assessment, contact us, or sign up for a plan.</p>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We also collect limited technical information automatically when you visit our site, such as your IP address, browser type, and pages viewed, to keep the site secure and understand how it's used.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We use your information to deliver and support the services you've requested, respond to your enquiries, send service-related communications, process payments, and improve our services. We do not use your information for unrelated purposes without your consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">4. Disclosure to Third Parties</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We do not sell your personal information. We share it only with trusted providers who help us deliver our services — such as hosting infrastructure, payment processors, and email delivery — and only to the extent needed to perform those services. These providers are bound to protect your information. We may also disclose information where required by law.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">5. Data Storage & Security</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We take reasonable steps to protect your information from misuse, loss, and unauthorised access, including secure infrastructure and a triple-redundant backup system. Some of our service providers may store data outside Australia; where this happens, we take reasonable steps to ensure your information remains protected.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">6. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Our website uses cookies and privacy-respecting analytics to understand traffic and improve the experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though some parts of the site may not function as intended.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">7. Accessing & Correcting Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">You can request access to the personal information we hold about you, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete it where we're able to. Just contact us and we'll respond within a reasonable timeframe.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">8. Complaints</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">If you believe we've mishandled your personal information, contact us first and we'll work to resolve it. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-brand-border pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Questions about this policy or your information? <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-accent-strong font-semibold hover:underline">Get in touch</a> and we'll help.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="callout-box mt-12">
        <p class="font-medium text-brand-dark mb-1">Internal note</p>
        <p class="text-brand-text-secondary text-sm">This privacy policy is a template and requires legal review before publication. [Internal: pending sign-off]</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
